ip thus came to see the revival experience as costly and ineffective.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 7aRELIGION / History.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978077357290440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780773572904423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780773572904/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles